title: Colorful River Landscape
description: A vibrant landscape featuring a river with striking red and orange hues, surrounded by lush green vegetation. The river's unusual colors suggest the presence of minerals or pollutants, contrasting sharply with the natural greenery of the trees and plants along the banks.

title: Rock Formations in Nature
description: A panoramic view of unique rock formations surrounded by lush greenery under a clear blue sky. The scene captures the rugged texture of the rocks, which vary in size and shape, creating a dramatic landscape.

title: Scenic Coastal View
description: A picturesque view of a coastal area featuring a calm blue water body, sandy shores, and lush green vegetation in the foreground. The horizon shows a clear sky, and there are small boats visible in the distance, suggesting a serene and inviting atmosphere.

title: Coastal Ruins
description: A scenic view of a coastal landscape featuring a sandy beach in the foreground, with lush green vegetation. In the background, there is an island with ruins of a building and a tower, surrounded by calm waters. A small boat is visible near the island, and the sky appears overcast.
